metadata.description: Mocaverse is the Animoca Brands membership NFT collection of 8,888 unique beings that thrive in unity: The Mocas. There are 5 incredible Moca tribes of the Angels, Builders, Dreamers, Connectors, and Neo-Capitalists. Join the Mocas in the realms to Learn, Play, Do Good, and Build together as we champion our Web3 values! Learn more about the Mocas at www.mocaverse.xyz.
